<title>UK: SmithKline hits new peak after ADRs climb.</title>
<headline>SmithKline hits new peak after ADRs climb.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in SmithKline Beecham rose to another record peak, tracking gains in its ADRs in the U.S. overnight, dealers said.</p>
<p>By 1145 GMT, the shares were up 10p to 756p. SmithKline's ADRs gained $1-1/4 to $59-3/8.</p>
<p>The UK pharmaceutical sector began rising again earlier this week amid renewed takeover talk.</p>
<p>&quot;It's been rising the last few days and hitting new highs the last few days, &quot; said one dealer. &quot;But there's no fresh news.&quot;</p>
<p>--Debra Sherman, London newsroom +44 171 542 4026</p>
